node.text: Massive 3 team trade between the Predators, Flyers, and Golden Knights.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 17, 2021. May be an image of ‎1 person, playing hockey, indoor and ‎text that says '‎CCM TRADE RECEIVES TORONTO MAPLE LEAFS っ JARED MCCANN مصم RECEIVES FILIP HALLANDER 7TH RD PICK ELLIOTTE ELLITTEE HOCKEY COLLECTIVE‎'‎‎.

node.text: The Maple Leafs have acquired Jared McCann from the Pittsburgh Penguins.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'TRADE HOCKEY COLLECTIVE RECEIVES RECEIVES ADIN HILL 7TH RD PICK JOSEF KORENAR 2ND RD PICK'.

node.text: Adin Hill is headed to the San Jose Sharks. Both picks are in 2022.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, playing hockey, indoor and text that says 'SIGNED Come MIRO HEISKANEN YEARS, $67.6M ($8.45MAAV) ($8.45M AAV) HOCKEY COLLECTIVE'.

node.text: Miro Heiskanen secures the bag from Dallas, signing an 8-year deal.
